    "engine": "knitr",
    "markdown": "# Mind Sized World Models\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\nThis chapter include models that breakdown, variate and extend Bardi's Mind Sized World Models. See original description and discussion [@bardi_mind_2013;@bardi_toward_2019].\n\n## One-Stock Model: constant rate\n\n### Description\n\n::: {layout=\"[[1,1], [1]]\"}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"grViz html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-818794617a177590d01d\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-818794617a177590d01d\">{\"x\":{\"diagram\":\"\\ndigraph onestock {\\n  \\n  # Node definitions\\n  Stock [shape = box, style = filled, fillcolor = lightblue]\\n  Sink [shape = circle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = salmon, width = 0.5]\\n  node [shape = plain]\\n    k1\\n  node [shape = invtriangle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = grey, width = 0.5]\\n    outflow\\n  \\n  # Edge definitions\\n  Stock -> outflow -> Sink [ penwidth = 5]\\n  k1 -> outflow [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  \\n  # Layout settings\\n  rankdir=TB\\n    \\n  # Position k1 perpendicular to the flow\\n  { rank=same; k1; outflow }\\n}\",\"config\":{\"engine\":\"dot\",\"options\":null}},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n$$\n\\frac{dS}{dt} = - k_1\n$$\n\n*Variables*:\n\n$S$: stock\n\n$k_1$: consumption/loss rate\n\n:::\n\n### Implementation\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](models-Bardi_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.svg)\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## One-Stock Model: density-dependent rate\n\n### Description\n\n::: {layout=\"[[1,1], [1]]\"}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"grViz html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-805f0a2bd06ed094ce19\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-805f0a2bd06ed094ce19\">{\"x\":{\"diagram\":\"\\ndigraph onestock {\\n  \\n  # Node definitions\\n  Stock [shape = box, style = filled, fillcolor = lightblue]\\n  Sink [shape = circle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = salmon, width = 0.5]\\n  node [shape = plain]\\n    k1\\n  node [shape = invtriangle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = grey, width = 0.5]\\n    outflow\\n  \\n  # Edge definitions\\n  Stock -> outflow -> Sink [ penwidth = 5]\\n  Stock -> outflow [ tailport = \\\"e\\\", headport = \\\"e\\\", constraint = false, style = dashed]\\n  k1 -> outflow [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  \\n  # Layout settings\\n  rankdir=TB\\n    \\n  # Position k1 perpendicular to the flow\\n  { rank=same; k1; outflow }\\n}\",\"config\":{\"engine\":\"dot\",\"options\":null}},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n$$\n\\frac{dS}{dt} = - k_1 \\cdot S(t)\n$$\n\n*Variables*:\n\n$S$: stock\n\n$k_1$: consumption/loss rate\n\n:::\n\n### Implementation\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](models-Bardi_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-10-1.svg)\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## One-Stock Model: density-dependent rate, renewable\n\n### Description\n\n::: {layout=\"[[1,1], [1]]\"}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"grViz html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-665178d9aceb151ae851\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-665178d9aceb151ae851\">{\"x\":{\"diagram\":\"\\ndigraph onestock {\\n  \\n  # Node definitions\\n  Stock [shape = box, style = filled, fillcolor = lightblue]\\n  Source [shape = circle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = lightyellow, width = 0.5]\\n  Sink [shape = circle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = salmon, width = 0.5]\\n  node [shape = plain]\\n    k0 k1\\n  node [shape = invtriangle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = grey, width = 0.5]\\n    inflow outflow\\n  \\n  # Edge definitions\\n  Source -> inflow -> Stock -> outflow -> Sink [ penwidth = 5]\\n  Stock -> outflow [ tailport = \\\"e\\\", headport = \\\"e\\\", constraint = false, style = dashed]\\n  k0 -> inflow [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  k1 -> outflow [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  \\n  # Layout settings\\n  rankdir=TB\\n    \\n  # Position k0 and k1 perpendicular to the flow\\n  { rank=same; k0; inflow }\\n  { rank=same; k1; outflow }\\n}\",\"config\":{\"engine\":\"dot\",\"options\":null}},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n$$\n\\frac{dS}{dt} = k_0 - k_1 \\cdot S(t)\n$$\n\n*Variables*:\n\n$S$: stock\n\n$k_0$: growth rate\n\n$k_1$: consumption/loss rate\n\n::: {layout=\"[[1,1], [1]]\"}\n\n### Implementation\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](models-Bardi_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-14-1.svg)\n:::\n:::\n\n\n### Reproducing Figure 3 in @bardi_mind_2013\n\nk0 = 0, k1 = 5 × 10−3, Stock(init) = 1\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](models-Bardi_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-18-1.svg)\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Two-Stock Model\n\n### Description\n\n::: {layout=\"[[1,1], [1]]\"}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"grViz html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-5d6257ada931329b32da\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-5d6257ada931329b32da\">{\"x\":{\"diagram\":\"\\ndigraph onestock {\\n  \\n  # Node definitions\\n  Stock1 [shape = box, style = filled, fillcolor = lightblue, label = \\\"Natural Resources\\\"]\\n  Stock2 [shape = box, style = filled, fillcolor = lightblue, label = \\\"Industrial Capital\\\"]\\n  Source [shape = circle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = lightyellow, width = 0.5]\\n  Sink1 [shape = circle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = salmon, width = 0.5]\\n  Sink2 [shape = circle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = salmon, width = 0.5]\\n  node [shape = plain]\\n    k0 k1 k2 k3\\n  node [shape = invtriangle, label = \\\"\\\", style = filled, fillcolor = grey, width = 0.5]\\n    inflow1 outflow1 interflow12 outflow2\\n  \\n  # Edge definitions\\n  Source -> inflow1 -> Stock1 -> outflow1 -> Sink1 [ penwidth = 5]\\n                       Stock1 -> interflow12 -> Stock2 -> outflow2 -> Sink2 [ penwidth = 5]\\n  Stock1 -> outflow1 [ tailport = \\\"w\\\", headport = \\\"w\\\", constraint = false, style = dashed]\\n  Stock1 -> interflow12 [ tailport = \\\"e\\\", headport = \\\"e\\\", constraint = false, style = dashed]\\n  Stock2 -> interflow12 [ tailport = \\\"e\\\", headport = \\\"e\\\", constraint = false, style = dashed]\\n  Stock2 -> outflow2 [ tailport = \\\"e\\\", headport = \\\"e\\\", constraint = false, style = dashed]\\n  \\n  k0 -> inflow1 [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  k1 -> interflow12 [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  k2 -> outflow2 [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  k3 -> outflow1 [ constraint = false, style = dashed, minlen = 3]\\n  \\n  # Layout settings\\n  rankdir=TB\\n    \\n  # Position k0, k1, k2, k3 perpendicular to the flow\\n  { rank=same; k0; inflow1 }\\n  { rank=same; k1; interflow12 }\\n  { rank=same; k2; outflow2 }\\n  { rank=same; k3; outflow1 }\\n  { rank=same; Sink1; Sink2 }\\n}\",\"config\":{\"engine\":\"dot\",\"options\":null}},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n$$\n\\frac{dR}{dt} = k_0 - k_1 \\cdot R(t) \\cdot N(t) - k_3 \\cdot R(t)\n$$\n$$\n\\frac{dN}{dt} = k_1 \\cdot R(t) \\cdot N(t) - k_2 \\cdot N(t)\n$$\n\n*Variables*:\n\n$R$: Natural resource (stock)\n\n$N$: Industrial capital (stock)\n\n$k_0$: Natural resource renewal rate\n\n$k_1$: Natural resource consumption rate\n\n$k_2$: Industrial capital loss rate\n\n$k_3$: Natural resource loss rate\n\n:::\n\n### Implementation\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](models-Bardi_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-22-1.svg)\n:::\n:::\n\n### Reproducing Figure 5 in @bardi_mind_2013\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](models-Bardi_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-25-1.svg)\n:::\n:::\n",
